quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  18,1,"“Kutamandidwa konse kwabwino nkwa Allah, Yemwe adavumbulutsa kwa kapolo Wake (Mtumiki Muhammad{s.a.w}), buku (ili lopatulika), ndipo sadalikhotetse (koma m’menemo muli zoona zokhazokha)"
  18,2,"“(Walichita kukhala) loongoka kuti lichenjeze anthu za chilango chokhwima chochokera kwa Iye (Allah), ndikuti liwasangalatse okhulupirira omwe akuchita zabwino, kuti adzapeza malipiro abwino"
  18,3,“Adzakhalamo (mumtendere wosathawo) muyaya
  18,4,"“Ndikuti liwachenjeze amene akunena (kuti): “Allah wadzipangira Mwana.”"
  18,5,“Iwo pabodza lawolo alibe kuzindikira chinthu chilichonse chanzeru ngakhale makolo awo. Lakula kwabasi liwu lomwe likutuluka mkamwa mwawo. Sanena china koma bodza basi
  18,6,“Mwina udziwononga wekha pakuwadandaulira chikhalidwe chawo kuti sakhulupirira nkhani iyi. (Iyayi! Usakhale wodandaula ndi zimenezo)
  18,7,"“Ndithu Ife tazichita zomwe zili pamwamba pa nthaka kukhala zokometsera nthakayo, ndikuti (mwa izo) tiwayese mayeso kuti (ndani) mwa iwo ali wochita zabwino kwambiri"
  18,8,“Ndipo ndithu Ife ndi Amene tidzazichita zomwe zili pamenepo kukhala monga nthaka yoguga (yopanda mmera)
  18,9,"“Kodi ukuganiza kuti eni phanga ndi eni nkhani zomwe zidalembedwa m’mabuku, adali mwa zizindikiro zathu zododometsa kwambiri? (Iyayi, zilipo zododometsa kwabasi kuposa zimenezo)"
  18,10,"“Pamene anyamata adathawira kuphanga nati: “Mbuye wathu! Tipatseni chifundo chochokera kwa Inu, ndipo tikonzereni chiongoko m’zochita zathu.”"
  18,11,"“Tidagonthetsa makutu awo, (ndikugona kosamva nako kanthu) kwa zaka zambirimbiri m’phanga"
  18,12,"“Kenako tidawautsa, kuti tiwayese (kuti) ndani mwa magulu awiriwa amadziwa kuwerengera nthawi imene (anyamatawa) adakhala (m’phangamo)"